data.text:
```
update 
chi_product
join `chi_product_n_category` on chi_product_n_category.`product_id` = chi_product.id
join `chi_category` on chi_category.`id` = chi_product_n_category.category_id
set chi_product.category_name = chi_category.title
where
chi_product_n_category.`record_is_parent` = 1;


select chi_product.code,chi_product.name,chi_product.sale_price,chi_product.category_name,count(sa_inoutput_item.id) from chi_product 
inner join `sa_inoutput_item` on sa_inoutput_item.`product_id` = chi_product.id
inner join `sa_inoutput` on sa_inoutput.`id` = sa_inoutput_item.`inoutput_id`
where 
sa_inoutput.`create_time` >= "2020-11-01 00:00:00"
and 
sa_inoutput.`create_time` <= "2021-02-01 00:00:00"
group by chi_product.code;
```

#Challenge plank + nhảy dây.


##Thể thức cuộc thi: 

    - Kết hợp plank + Nhảy dây
	- Plank: 2 phút 
	- Nhảy dây: 6 phút - đạt tối thiểu 300 cái
